##Diary of the outbreak | the fifth day of the siege of Wuhan

Plantifulsoul

Introduction to behindmylife

2020.1.27

* The diary was originally scheduled to be posted yesterday, but it came to grief. The only notebook was flooded, and the follow-up was improper. The screen is not showing at present, and the touch bar is not responding. It is probable that the hardware is short-circuited. In such an emergency period as the city being sealed, call customer service, wuhan and Xi'an maintenance points are closed, not sure when to resume, complete repair may be in April... first to say sorry to everyone, short-term push with fate, now only a cell phone, think still have to survive the long ban, harm.

The fifth day of the city, the rain stopped, in the home "closed" a few days really to the limit, reading plays to eat sleep, thunderbolt fixed arrangements, boring and depressed. The weather forecast says it will be sunny for the next few days. When the sun comes out, go to the nearby park to bask in the sun.

I watched the press conference in Hubei Province, the interview with the Mayor of Wuhan, and it really made me laugh. It was a black comedy sketch, as if to bring some joy to the dull lives of the people at home (the image of Hubei Province rubs on the ground over and over) .

Wuhan issued a notice more than a person at a loss, suddenly ordered to stop motor vehicles travel, strengthen control, and in the crowd under questioning even hit the patch, to receive the notice of not allowed to go on the street, the rest normal; And asked the residents in isolation at home to hang signs, and then under the ridicule of users silently delete, day after day, patting the head casually decided that there is no forward-looking, I have been from the initial anger to numbness, when the joke.

These days and students about riding a bicycle, everyone's concern and blessings have been received, thank you, I also decided to self-intervention, do not so sad, go out for air, change the mood. Fresh from the rain, with little traffic and fresh air (though you can't smell it with a mask, it's all in your head) , we pedaled slowly through the empty streets, talking at a higher volume.

There are many people on the road, either on foot or riding a small blue bike, the rhythm of national fitness. Vehicles also have, gas stations normal refueling, taxi all hit the "suspension of business" sign, the traffic police on duty at all junctions, such as a red light when you see a stop to ask, but soon let go.

On the road is the highest cleaning workers, every few hundred meters there are 1-2, wearing a mask, protective measures in place. Even if the city martial law, they still stand in earnest every shift, the streets are not a lot of people, in fact, there is no garbage, mostly leaves, the masters of a round to find the nearest subway to sit down to rest.

On Weibo, many people said that the convenience store was open, so they went to two nearby convenience stores, both of which were not open. I thought the boiled glutinous corn in the convenience store was better prepared and sweeter than the ones I bought.

Box Horse Normal Business, I asked the staff how they work, told me to schedule as far as possible to consider the staff home, try to arrange to live near the early come, we can ride a small blue car or electric car can arrive in time. The holidays are open from 9:00 to 18:00, although there's nothing new at 2:00 or 3:00 p.m.

Vegetable is the food of relative shortage at present, kind is little, supply also reduces, before noon only mushroom, fruit is sufficient however. But we are all short of green leafy vegetables, not resistant to put, unlike rice, oil and meat, can be a lot of hoarding.

The staff told me that when the door opened at 9 am, the first batch of customers waiting at the door bought green vegetables. By 10:30 am, the green vegetables were almost sold out in the whole line, and the online transportation capacity was even tighter. Orders were limited to an alarm clock at 12 am.

Seafood and aquatic areas completely unpopular, hairy crabs in the pool, shrimp also climbed tiger style, I went to see the tank of turbot, still not used to this fish looks, too alien characteristics.

Downstairs, a row of doll machine lights up, look closely, scan code to buy money can play, but I always bad luck, put a pile of money can not catch the doll want to be.

The provincial library has put up notices to close the library, there is no notice when the library will resume. In the past, there were many children who went to the provincial library to do their winter vacation homework, young people preparing for exams and reading books. There will be a large row of shared bicycles parked at the entrance, and at 5 or 6 pm, all of them will be scanning codes and riding bicycles, now there are only three lonely "good new year" .

In front of the door is a garbage can for recycling face masks. It is empty. After watching the video of "recycling face masks for sale" on the Internet, the face masks are torn.

Some students in the system has been informed on the third day of normal work, look at the government departments on the street, it seems that no one, the gatekeeper uncle is still at work, and I stare through the glass.

The construction site all stopped working, looked through the baffle, the mound all took the net cover well, conforms to the standard ha ha.

I rode to Shahu Park with my classmates, this park is rather small, usually there is no one, it is suitable for walking the dog, walking around for a few rounds is very relaxing, we found a bench to sit and chat, haven't seen for a long time, a lot of words, today is a bit cold, we talked and rubbed our hands together and shook our legs.

Passing by a fresh food store, I thought it was not open, because the notice said that only large supermarkets were still open, such as the Zhongbaiwu store, box horse, and I came close to find an entrance, and I entered the Holes, the goods were full, and there were residents who were selecting vegetables, the only Greens left are cabbage and Celery, with plenty of seasoning (scallions, ginger, garlic, coriander) .

Wanda Plaza is silent and a bit scary from a distance. The notice posted on the door said to open on January 30, feeling unlikely, Fengcheng at least got the first 10 yuan Xiao Bar, even open the door, no one dare to go shopping.

I am not used to the empty streets of Han. During the Spring Festival, people should be crowded and chirped. There are people taking photos everywhere, carrying big bags and small bags in their hands. At this time, they have to hold on to their bags tightly for fear of thieves, and they have to worry about being trampled on dirty shoes, today, no one cares if I lie on my back in the middle of the road.

Suddenly there was a new idea to take photos of scenic spots. The masses in Wuhan had many ideas. They saw two middle-aged couples enjoying themselves. One took a photo with each other, and the other ran to the big stage to do Tai Chi and dance. They were a little happy to see the four people posing for a video shot, to the lifeless Han street into a breath of life, as if the moment cut into a silent film high-definition dazzle color.

Little Pomeranian put on a mask.

Light curtain is a place where many young people love to take photos. It fills up the light automatically and looks like a fairy. Every time we walk this way, we can see many girls using cell phones and Selfie sticks to instruct their boyfriends how to take good photos of her.

Meet a man holding a DSLR, should be a reporter source bar, we look at each other, eyes are curious, and then tacitly around an s, to avoid facing.

Unexpectedly, the large screen at the entrance of Wanda movie park still plays the popular science video in a round-robin manner, telling everyone how to detect the network fraud. I stood for a while to see, feel a little ugly animation, content is good, simple and easy to understand, suitable for the transmission of elders.

These days can always hear the street cat Howl, a listen is hungry call, a total of seven or eight cats in the community, mostly orange cat. In fact, some residents feed them. I don't know if the aunt who fed them left before the city was closed, or if she stayed at home all the time and didn't come out to see the way the cats were barking. She hasn't had a full meal for a long time. Moreover, recently, the cleaning staff are more diligent in taking out the garbage, and the trash cans are empty, cats can't even dig up leftovers.

I tried to shout a few times, unfamiliar with me, all hiding under the chassis of the car, went home to add some fish and sausage, originally want to get some dog food, express delivery can not come in, dog food also dare not give freely. Putting the leftovers in their empty bowls, the furry children raced around in a circle, their tails wagging, mewing, hoping they would survive the winter. There's an orange cat that looks familiar, a regular in the neighborhood, maybe 2 or 3 years old, and the rest of the orange cats are probably his kids.

Tomorrow, ride the other way with your classmates, and take advantage of the city before someone else does. I saw on the Internet that there have been quite a few statements that have rejected the Wuhan / Hubei Nationality, especially after the official announcement that "five million people have left the city, " which has intensified the panic and antagonism. I hope that everyone will treat these villagers from other places with tolerance, they are mostly home-bound students and migrant workers on early holidays. Due to the delay and concealment of official disclosure, no one knows the seriousness of the epidemic, and no one has informed them that they need to pay attention, these Hubei People in the field are also the victims of this epidemic, not everyone with malice and luck to "escape. ". Wuhan / Hubei is not the same as the pneumonia virus, we have more empathy, give a helping hand, guide them to carry out the right protection and isolation, thank you again!
